msgid "Plasma Camera"
msgstr "प्लाज्मा कैमरा"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.plasma.camera.appdata.xml:9
msgid "Take photos and videos"
msgstr "फोटो, विडियो च गृह्यताम्"

